sources.title: Room For Rent | Full Movie | Lin Shaye | Slasher Horror Movie | Horror Halloween Movie
sources.description:
Lonely widow Joyce rents out a room in her house and becomes dangerously obsessed with a younger guest. All Joyce is looking for is a decent man and when she thinks she's found one, will kill anyone that stands in her way of happiness.
2019.  Stars: Lin Shaye, Oliver Rayon, Valeska Mosich Miller
